{"tid":719180,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】最美女球迷現真身　否認是AV女優　曾當選莫斯科小姐","createTime":"2018-06-27T08:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T16:15:25.000Z","uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a26fcd1f171a1813fc4b1026a0ad6db552bed9c","tid":719180,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"人生總少不免被人誤會，就像被喻為今屆世界盃最美的俄羅斯女球迷Natalya Nemchinova，一度被起底指是AV女星，不過日前她便公開現身否認。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的Natalya於訪問中指，自己曾在年輕時拍攝過性感寫真，包括一些露點照片，惟並沒有拍攝三級影片：「我從未入行色情工業，所有報道都不是事實。」據她透露其前男友有一段兩人的私密影片，並於5年前分手時將片段上載到網絡報復，當近日有網民將Natalya起底後，其私密影片自然再被發掘出來。<br />\n<br />\nNatalya指自己是長期足球球迷，最近才知道被人起底：「我沒有上網的習慣，都是朋友向我透露才知道此事。」現在她只想故事盡快完結：「我不希望被人視為色情片女主角，不過整個世界相信了別的事。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然Natalya沒有拍攝色情影片，惟色情網站「Pornhub」上的熱門搜尋，頭5位有2位都是關於Natalya的。另外，又有網民發現Natalya於2007年被選為莫斯科小姐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1585165/org/48650cbace6b7d57abf420afddd260e6.jpg/FMh0pnV_AGBNIEuHD0i7jL7RnuTt0GiWybv0Icm79CE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1585165%2Forg%2F48650cbace6b7d57abf420afddd260e6.jpg%2FFMh0pnV_AGBNIEuHD0i7jL7RnuTt0GiWybv0Icm79CE&h=28e41d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1563759/org/2faa79556aff3595fe13bf98bb502428.jpeg/Qw2hsofjFufrzPUvY34e4obUFdXDHX_u-56RnPuekZw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1563759%2Forg%2F2faa79556aff3595fe13bf98bb502428.jpeg%2FQw2hsofjFufrzPUvY34e4obUFdXDHX_u-56RnPuekZw&h=20284438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1585169/org/c0882351622b2250b5daf72d020c7c8d.jpg/EMtvGu4PU_K5v4j0DuHsjBP4rA1A1ywNWer4D1nq-A8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1585169%2Forg%2Fc0882351622b2250b5daf72d020c7c8d.jpg%2FEMtvGu4PU_K5v4j0DuHsjBP4rA1A1ywNWer4D1nq-A8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2602c2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有指Natalya於2007年被選為莫斯科小姐。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"d3e6602fdf9bbbcfa858efc7de60ec105c56e1b1","tid":719180,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"有晒片都唔係佢？"},{"pid":"cc01d14cac80fe1e512e6e35b5c4ab8de1ffa15c","tid":719180,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"枉我射咗幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c22f134f5bac08b797a33b1d3d83f576b024794","tid":719180,"uid":60303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"95f6fb02dfae8fd70a02656aab0d4cbb75a8306a","tid":719180,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc01d14cac80fe1e512e6e35b5c4ab8de1ffa15c","tid":719180,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"枉我射咗幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"係咪av女優同你射左幾次有咩關係牙"},{"pid":"60343eceb2e2bddb4fcc9a11e02a1923c70888db","tid":719180,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"第一張好醜樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa423948ab89c8178e74193e73084ac22fe4a343","tid":719180,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649d5262ec7de5976637afb7aa25a1464f36063c","tid":719180,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji